# Local-only shell config (machine-private / work) — never tracked in the public
# dotfiles. Holds loose NN-*.sh snippets + cloned private repos (each sourced via
# its *.plugin.zsh entrypoint). Populated locally (Phase 2: a private git-repo external).
.config/zsh/private/
.config/zsh/.antidote/
.config/zsh/.zsh_plugins.zsh
.config/zsh/.zcompdump*
